Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.50,Caption,,0,0,0,,Why do they prioritize certain projects?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:02.34,Caption,,0,0,0,,How do they think about their work
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.34,0:00:03.20,Caption,,0,0,0,,and where they wanna end up in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.20,0:00:04.06,Caption,,0,0,0,,the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.06,0:00:05.44,Caption,,0,0,0,,Being curious about your customers and your
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:06.82,Caption,,0,0,0,,team
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.82,0:00:08.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,is how you develop a different mental
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.04,0:00:09.26,Caption,,0,0,0,,model
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.26,0:00:10.62,Caption,,0,0,0,,to be able to solve problems that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.62,0:00:11.98,Caption,,0,0,0,,are more effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.98,0:00:13.64,Caption,,0,0,0,,Even more importantly to that is asking
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.64,0:00:15.30,Caption,,0,0,0,,yourself why.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.30,0:00:16.74,Caption,,0,0,0,,Why do you react that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.74,0:00:18.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,Why do you feel anger when those
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:19.34,Caption,,0,0,0,,situations happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:20.82,Caption,,0,0,0,,What gets you frustrated?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.82,0:00:22.26,Caption,,0,0,0,,I always say, the world will show
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.26,0:00:23.70,Caption,,0,0,0,,you where you're not free.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.70,0:00:25.26,Caption,,0,0,0,,A life unexamined is a life that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.26,0:00:26.82,Caption,,0,0,0,,wasn't lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.82,0:00:28.21,Caption,,0,0,0,,For you to truly express yourself in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.21,0:00:29.60,Caption,,0,0,0,,business
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.60,0:00:31.10,Caption,,0,0,0,,with your family, with your friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.10,0:00:33.22,Caption,,0,0,0,,you have to understand who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:34.56,Caption,,0,0,0,,Even today, I was just recently at
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.56,0:00:35.90,Caption,,0,0,0,,one of my mentors,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.90,0:00:37.18,Caption,,0,0,0,,Patrick Bette David's office,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:37.96,Caption,,0,0,0,,and I saw a poster on the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.96,0:00:38.74,Caption,,0,0,0,,wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:39.90,Caption,,0,0,0,,and I asked one of the sales
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:41.06,Caption,,0,0,0,,guys, what's that poster?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:42.42,Caption,,0,0,0,,And he told me that it's all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.42,0:00:43.78,Caption,,0,0,0,,the goals of the business,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:44.84,Caption,,0,0,0,,and the way it works is that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.84,0:00:45.90,Caption,,0,0,0,,if the bottom people
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:47.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,don't hit their goal, because there was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.04,0:00:48.18,Caption,,0,0,0,,a reward next to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.18,0:00:49.12,Caption,,0,0,0,,the people at the top don't get
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.12,0:00:50.06,Caption,,0,0,0,,theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.06,0:00:51.16,Caption,,0,0,0,,And I thought to myself, how simple
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.16,0:00:52.25,Caption,,0,0,0,,of an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.08,0:00:02.80,Hook,,0,0,0,,How do they think about their work and where they wanna end up in the future? Being curious about your customers and your team is how you develop a different mental model to be able to solve problems that are more effective. Even more importantly to that is asking yourself why. Why do you react that way? Why do you feel anger when those situations happens? What gets you frustrated? I always say, the world will show you where you're not free. A life unexamined is a life that wasn't lived. For you to truly express yourself in business with your family, with your friends, you have to understand who you are. Even today, I was just recently at one of my mentors, Patrick Bette David's office, and I saw a poster on the wall, and I asked one of the sales guys, what's that poster? And he told me that it's all the goals of the business, and the way it works is that if the bottom people don't hit their goal, because there was a reward next to it, the people at the top don't get theirs. And I thought to myself, how simple of an idea to get everybody aligned in the business with their goals across different departments. I took that idea, I created the aligned goals ladder
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.45,0:00:52.05,CTA,,0,0,0,,#your #about #their #where
Dialogue: 2,0:00:49.65,0:00:52.15,CTA,,0,0,0,,Follow for more creator breakdowns